28:23.036 --> 28:24.661
Put the box over there

28:26.873 --> 28:28.040
Yes. lt's good there

28:50.647 --> 28:52.690
Turn the volume down

28:54.401 --> 28:56.443
l wish he loved me

28:57.862 --> 28:59.363
ln your dreams

28:59.614 --> 29:02.199
l'd have my own hotel

29:03.284 --> 29:05.369
