You take out the inside

35:23.581 --> 35:24.581
Hold it like this

35:26.793 --> 35:27.626
Where are you from?

35:28.169 --> 35:29.962
l'm from Ossian. Have you heard of it?

35:30.088 --> 35:31.088
No

35:31.631 --> 35:33.841
l don't think anything
can happen staying here

35:34.092 --> 35:35.300
Why are you saying that?

35:35.552 --> 35:37.094
lt's not so good here

35:37.220 --> 35:38.804
l have big dreams

35:38.930 --> 35:41.974
Be the manager of a big hotel

35:42.809 --> 35:44.351
l am thinking about moving country

35:44.519 --> 35:45.811
Solid planning

36:05.707 --> 36:06.957
Sir is in the bedroom

37:27.330 --> 37:29.248
This pair will match

37:31.626 --> 37:32.626
How do they look?

37:38.133 --> 37:39.633
lt's me Trishna

37:40.719 --> 37:41.552
l'm not sure

37:42.053 --> 37:43.721
l think we are just passing the market

37:46.808 --> 37:48.142
This is my friend Chanchal

37:48.852 --> 37:51.270
Chanchal these are all my friends
from College

38:19.466 --> 38:22.926
Hey guys! l was thinking
it's nearly over here

38:23.053 --> 38:26.055
should we go out somewhere?

38:28.350 --> 38:30.017
Some parties are long, some are short

38:31.853 --> 38:32.811
Casbah?

38:33.146 --> 38:34.521
How about it?

38:39.778 --> 38:42.488
Come on. We've already
told the boss we'll be back by 9

38:42.614 --> 38:43.822
Relax

38:44.574 --> 38:45.532
OK l'm going on my own

38:45.825 --> 38:46.784
- You'll be OK right?
- Yes

38:46.951 --> 38:48.535
OK take care

38:53.625 --> 38:55.793
She worries too much

39:14.187 --> 39:15.187
Stop!

39:26.366 --> 39:27.825
Who are you calling?

39:29.035 --> 39:30.661
You can use my phone

39:32.539 --> 39:33.706
Leave me alone

39:35.000 --> 39:36.500
