39:40.463 --> 39:41.922
What's your problem?

39:45.301 --> 39:46.135
Look at you

39:46.261 --> 39:47.761
You haven't got any balls

41:50.260 --> 41:57.224
Where were you?

41:58.143 --> 41:59.601
Go to sleep

42:00.770 --> 42:02.479
Jay phoned me after you left

42:06.067 --> 42:07.818
He was looking for you

42:12.240 --> 42:13.240
l rang you

