42:23.168 --> 42:24.877
Did he find you?

42:27.922 --> 42:28.922
What happened?

42:29.049 --> 42:31.008
l'm fine. Go to sleep

43:22.644 --> 43:25.979
Devshri

43:28.316 --> 43:29.817
How are you?

43:29.943 --> 43:31.026
You OK?

43:31.569 --> 43:32.736
How are you Lakshman?

43:32.862 --> 43:33.821
Did you forget me?

43:38.993 --> 43:40.160
You have time off work?

43:41.663 --> 43:42.496
Who is it?

43:42.622 --> 43:43.872
ls it Trishna?

43:49.587 --> 43:50.838
How are you?

43:51.965 --> 43:52.798
Fine

44:03.143 --> 44:04.768
Don't make it too strong

44:06.396 --> 44:07.688
How is school going?

44:07.814 --> 44:09.857
No l've left school now

44:09.983 --> 44:10.816
Why?

44:11.317 --> 44:13.235
We don't have money for the fees

44:13.903 --> 44:15.821
What happened to the money l sent you?

44:16.281 --> 44:18.449
