44:22.954 --> 44:24.371
How come you're here?

44:26.833 --> 44:28.250
l've left the hotel job

44:30.545 --> 44:31.420
What happened?

44:32.172 --> 44:33.589
l just had to leave

44:34.132 --> 44:35.299
Why?

44:37.093 --> 44:38.510
Dad l just had to

44:42.349 --> 44:43.766
