44:55.737 --> 44:56.737
l know

45:38.279 --> 45:39.113
What's happened?

45:39.197 --> 45:40.030
You OK?

45:40.532 --> 45:41.532
Bring some water

46:21.740 --> 46:22.990
Drink this

47:04.199 --> 47:05.741
She's not had her period

47:05.909 --> 47:07.326
Not had her period?

47:08.203 --> 47:09.578
How many months has it been?

47:09.746 --> 47:11.121
Three

47:11.247 --> 47:12.498
Three months?

47:13.625 --> 47:15.334
Any other problems?

47:15.585 --> 47:17.169
l'm sick in the mornings

48:09.347 --> 48:10.222
Here

48:25.655 --> 48:28.240
You have to go to your Uncle's
and get work in the factory

48:32.120 --> 48:34.079
l don't want to leave home again

48:36.291 --> 48:37.624
