48:38.543 --> 48:40.294
Dad says you have to go and help out

48:44.382 --> 48:46.133
l don't want to go away again

48:53.016 --> 48:55.768
Dad says that you have to

49:02.525 --> 49:03.525
OK

49:04.277 --> 49:05.903
lf that's what you want

49:44.734 --> 49:46.068
Mum

49:46.277 --> 49:47.736
l'm going now

49:52.575 --> 49:53.701
Look after yourself

49:54.953 --> 49:55.786
l'm going Grandma

49:57.622 --> 49:59.081
Bless you

50:03.378 --> 50:04.378
l'm going Dad

50:24.649 --> 50:25.691
What is it?

50:25.817 --> 50:27.609
l'm coming with you

50:28.278 --> 50:29.570
Don't be silly

50:30.447 --> 50:31.989
You can't come with me

50:33.158 --> 50:33.991
Let me go

51:29.130 --> 51:30.839
Where is this address?

51:32.467 --> 51:35.094
lt is just over there

51:50.068 --> 51:51.610
Uncle

51:51.861 --> 51:52.736
Bless you

51:53.279 --> 51:54.697
- How's everyone?
- OK

51:54.823 --> 51:55.656
How is your Dad?

51:55.782 --> 51:56.824
Good

51:58.118 --> 51:59.868
Gomti, Trishna is here

52:01.913 --> 52:03.247
Be happy child

52:03.873 --> 52:04.790
How are you?

52:05.083 --> 52:05.916
l'm not well

52:06.668 --> 52:08.085
lt's been 4 or 5 months

52:08.211 --> 52:09.878
l'm in so much pain

52:10.463 --> 52:13.549
My whole body hurts,
l can't even stand up

53:43.556 --> 53:45.099
YourAunt needs food, you're late

53:45.266 --> 53:47.142
Yes almost done

54:02.492 --> 54:04.451
Trishna, someone's here for you

54:04.577 --> 54:05.411
What?

54:05.453 --> 54:07.204
There's someone to see you

54:48.913 --> 54:52.875
Sir, may l take five minutes?

54:53.501 --> 54:54.626
OK

